org.bytedeco.bullet.BulletCollision

Class btBroadphaseProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.bullet.BulletCollision.btBroadphaseProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    btDbvtProxy, btSimpleBroadphaseProxy

    @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=BulletCollision.class)
public class btBroadphaseProxy
extends Pointer
    The btBroadphaseProxy is the main class that can be used with the Bullet broadphases. It stores collision shape type information, collision filter information and a client object, typically a btCollisionObject or btRigidBody.
